high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Take a step to the left to face the fridge.
Cut the apple in the fridge into 3 pieces.
Place the knife on the shelf above the apple in the fridge.
Pick up a piece of apple in the fridge.
Take a step to the left to face the microwave on the counter.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room and then turn to the left to face the white table.
Place the piece of apple on the edge of the white table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it on the edge of the white table.

high_descs: Go over to the white table and face it.
Pick up the knife that's in front of the egg.
Bring the knife over to the black fridge.
Open the fridge and use the knife to cut the apple on the bottom shelf.
Put the knife down on the top shelf.
Pick up a piece of the apple from the bottom shelf.
Bring the apple to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Cook the apple in the microwave and then take it out again.
Bring the apple over to the same white table where you got the knife.
Put the apple down on the edge of the table so that it's in front of the spatula and to the right of the phone.
anns.task_desc: Put warm apple on the table.

high_descs: Go to the white table
Pick up a butterknife from the table
Go to the fridge
Cut the apple in the fridge
Place the butterknife in the fridge
Pick up an apple slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple slice
Go to the big white table
Put the apple slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple slice on a table
